title: [Gyldemar Green, Forest]
description: Covering the top of this knoll is a large meadow.  Butterfly-weed, creeping phlox, asters and little bluestem blanket the area in color.  Butterflies and bees flit from flower to flower.

Covering the top of this knoll is a large meadow.  Butterfly-weed, creeping phlox, asters and little bluestem blanket the area in color.  Fireflies and moths flit from flower to flower in the moonlight.
